# Speed Test Mission
# Description: Tests airspeed changes during flight
#
# Mission Profile:
# - Takeoff to 100m
# - Set speed to 12 m/s (slow)
# - Fly north
# - Set speed to 18 m/s (fast)
# - Fly east
# - Set speed to 15 m/s (cruise)
# - Return and land
#
# Expected Duration: ~7 minutes
# Speed range: 12-18 m/s
#
# Usage:
#   wp load speed_test.waypoints
#   mode AUTO
#
# Good for:
# - TECS speed/altitude coupling
# - Throttle response
# - Airspeed sensor validation
#
# Watch parameters:
# - ARSPD_FBW_MIN (min airspeed)
# - ARSPD_FBW_MAX (max airspeed)
# - TRIM_ARSPD_CM (cruise airspeed)
# - TECS_SPDWEIGHT (speed vs altitude priority)
#
# Command 178 (DO_CHANGE_SPEED):
# - param1: 0 (airspeed type)
# - param2: target speed (m/s)
# - param3: throttle (-1 = no change)
#
# Author: Patrick Kelly (@Kuscko)
# Version: 1.0
